/**
 * Complex multi-drug prescription
 * Exercises warnings, conditionals, IV routes, timing, and multiple R/ blocks
 */

# --- Antibiotic (IV, weight-based) ---
R/ Gentamicine sol. inj. 5 mg/kg/dag
   BLACKBOX
Da/ disp. 5 ampullen
S/ 1dd i.v. mane
   sig. sec. art.
   d.i.m.m.

# --- Analgesic (PRN) ---
R/ Paracetamol 1000 mg tablet
   d.t.d. no 30
D/ disp. 30 tablets
S/ q.6h. p.r.n. bij pijn p.o.
   non rep.

# --- Inhaler ---
R/ Salbutamol 100 mcg/pufje aeros.
   LASA
Da/ disp. 1 stuks
S/ 1-2 pufjes q.4h. per inhalationem zo nodig
   p.r.n.
   rep. 3

/* Paediatric suspension — weight-based, with compounding */
R/ Amoxicilline          250 mg
   Aqua purificata q.s.  ad 5 ml
   m.f. susp.
D/ disp. 100 ml
S/ t.d.d. 5 ml p.o. p.c.
   CITO
